{"tid":1869782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國歌歌詞被列為禁語？  中國網民收通知「不願做奴隸的人們」為激進內容","createTime":"2020-02-08T11:09:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T11:36:40.000Z","uid":28114,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9662fa99f7b19e7ee2c86b93b930601518c5a01a","tid":1869782,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:09:25.000Z","msg":"中國網路被政府機關監視，而社交網絡的分享訊息，也會被所屬服務過濾審查。不過除了反動、反政府內容被禁制外，近來似乎有更廣泛內容被列為敏感內容。近日就有網民發圖，指收到通知，中國國歌其中一段歌詞被列為激進內容，被該服務移除。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/螢幕截圖_2020-02-08_下午5_06_24.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96_2020-02-08_%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%885_06_24.png&h=061cd423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/螢幕截圖-2020-02-08-下午5.06.28.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-02-08-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%885.06.28.png&h=8918f4f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有中國網民發表了一張未知是本人還是轉載的圖片，內容為一條由中國社交網絡豆瓣所發出的通知，內容提到「你發佈的動態『起來不願做奴隸的人們』或該動態分享的內容由於含有激進時政或意識形態方面的內容，現已被移除」。訊息中也提到如果發言多次被刪除的話，帳號擁有者可能會受到禁言或刪除帳戶的處分。<br />\n<br />\n根據豆瓣的「社區指導原則」資料， 寫明「激進時政或意識形態方面的內容」屬於「不歡迎」的內容，屬於受禁制內容的次一級。同被列為「不歡迎」的內容有「針對種族、國家、民族、宗教、性別、年齡、地緣、性取向、生理特徵的歧視和仇恨言論」、「未經授權洩露他人隱私的行為」等等。<br />\n<br />\n而「指導原則」最受限制的為「不允許」之內容，則包括有「危害國家安全，洩露國家秘密，顛覆國家政權，破壞國家統一」，還有「損害國家榮譽和利益」等 17 項有關中國國家利益與他人合法權益的內容。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/02/08/douban/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F02%2F08%2Fdouban%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOg9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=933f158e\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/02/08/douban/tech-secure/</a>"},{"pid":"9e5ead8d87e2a920e2d1c59dbbf5800144a17c9b","tid":1869782,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:12:11.000Z","msg":"支那國歌好激進<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e996605fba111133009f76dadd707905072404c","tid":1869782,"uid":220942,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:13:26.000Z","msg":"一直都懷疑啲大陸人唔明歌詞講咩"},{"pid":"a4666e72dc884789b22ecc650d6b8951c6911480","tid":1869782,"uid":69746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:14:33.000Z","msg":"愛國但唔俾唱國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9e0534c6aae3d1cb8d5e65a3d448a24125b018","tid":1869782,"uid":19176,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:14:44.000Z","msg":"班支那人真係唔明中國國歌歌詞點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb11d3ef6b3e56cf79b821f213e533c14ccaa30","tid":1869782,"uid":313584,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:17:23.000Z","msg":"諗起班仆街死都要立國歌法<br />\n真係好撚諷刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4742f827457556c5d3dfe37c198c497b7369c56a","tid":1869782,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:18:09.000Z","msg":"改唱<br />\n吾黨所忠<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d238db20779a2b0feb91076d383d4fda393872","tid":1869782,"uid":270835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:20:35.000Z","msg":"本身支那國歌就係諷刺，聽親都笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e03d5720cf0e1e78b503518fcf1caf5665a0e0b","tid":1869782,"uid":161025,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:33:21.000Z","msg":"推翻自己首歌應該係世界第一國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ff202ccffd717089129a4d0a1c4f77603fe7bc","tid":1869782,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:36:17.000Z","msg":"支国国歌根本係革命神曲<br />\n<br />\n每句都鼓勵緊人搞勇武革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e94fff96ad692c81398ff296d23a59fcb4caef","tid":1869782,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:36:40.000Z","msg":"舉着紅旗反紅旗<br />\n支那一早唔理咗呢套混水<br />\n邊個拳頭硬就邊個係道理"}]}